Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:55.67,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,0)}I've still got a lot of years ahead of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:01:57.67,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\pos(640,700)}{\alpha&HFF&}To just erase these fee{\alpha&H00&}lings?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:01:57.63,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\pos(640,700)}{\alpha&HFF&}To just erase {\alpha&H00&}these feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:57.59,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\pos(640,700)}To just erase these feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:00.68,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,0)}I want to go back and finish
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:04.31,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,489)}The things that I've yet to finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:20.57,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,489)}I was supposed to be chasing after my ongoing dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:26.91,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,0)}Yet I faltered over others while walking this thin, winding path.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:30.08,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's not that I want to return to those days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:33.59,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm searching for the sky I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:35.25,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Don't make that sad face, as if you've fallen victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:40.47,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}As if you want people to pity you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:42.18,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Tears aren't the end of your sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:43.85,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You have to bear them painfully, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:45.51,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Who are you waiting for in the maze of emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:47.18,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Where you can't even see the exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:48.98,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I want to blurt it out more justly,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:50.73,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Just like how I wrote it in my white notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:52.40,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What do you want to run from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:54.02,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}That thing called "reality"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:57.36,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I just want to scream out,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:03:00.78,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}"I'm only living to fulfill my wish." Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:04.91,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,489)}I can't take the safe way out of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:07.70,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I don't even have a place to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:11.00,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm always thankful for everyone's kindness,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:14.38,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}That's why I want to become stronger. (I'm on the way)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.34,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}This is reminding me of the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:19.59,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,889)}This pain is all right with me.
